{
  "stem": "3666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably about 11, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] actually, I don't remember how we separated from that particular camp because at one point, they took a whole transport away to a different camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, we went to a different camp, too, and that different camp meant again going by train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually it was more than by train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were on a- in a boat, and we were in a boat for about two days, the bottom of the boat, going to Riga.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were full of lice, and, we-- of course, we had no hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But our clothing, we would sit at night and do this, you know, get rid of the lice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to put some kind of a smelly thing on us or on our clothes-- I don't know what it was-- to get rid of the lice, but we still had lice.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could never understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Perhaps from weakness, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were full of lice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would take clothes, I think, and and they would go through some kind of a process.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it didn't matter because we didn't-- as soon as you put it back on, you were full of lice again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we got it from each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As far as toilets, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every time you needed a toilet, there was maybe one or two toilets in the entire barrack, and there were always lines.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if you were unfortunate, you had some problem with dysentery, you were very unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was horror.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then you got beaten.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, oh, of course, a lot of people got sick and died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The barrack was not clear of death every single day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every single day, people were dying.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
